<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الطَّهَارَةِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَهِيَ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- ارْتِفَاعُ الحَدَثِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَزَوَالُ الخَبَثِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَالمِيَاهُ ثَلَاثَةٌ:</span> طَهُورٌ، وَطَاهِرٌ، وَنَجِسٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> فَالطَّهُورُ: هُوَ البَاقِي عَلَى خِلْقَتِهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- طَهُورٌ فِي نَفْسِهِ، مُطَهِّرٌ لِغَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- يَجُوزُ اسْتِعْمَالُهُ مُطْلَقًا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٢]</span> وَالطَّاهِرُ:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- مَا تَغَيَّرَ كَثِيرٌ مِنْ لَوْنِهِ، أَوْ طَعْمِهِ، أَوْ رِيحِهِ بِطَاهِرٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَهُوَ طَاهِرٌ فِي نَفْسِهِ، غَيْرُ مُطَهِّرٍ لِغَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> يَجُوزُ اسْتِعْمَالُهُ فِي غَيْرِ:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- رَفْعِ حَدَثٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- وَزَوَالِ خَبَثٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span style="color:#707070">[٣]</span> وَالنَّجِسُ: مَا تَغَيَّرَ بِنَجَاسَةٍ فِي غَيْرِ مَحَلِّ تَطْهِيرٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>